data.description:
Welcome home! This 4-bedroom lakefront retreat, offers a perfect blend of comfort and style.

Step into the heart of the home, where a spacious open floor plan adorned with elegant crown molding awaits. The kitchen, a chef's delight, boasts pendant lighting, granite countertops, an island with a sink, and not one, but two inviting eating areas. Whether you're hosting a dinner party or enjoying a quiet family meal, this kitchen is designed to impress.

The master suite is a sanctuary of tranquility, featuring double tray ceilings that add an extra touch of sophistication. Natural light floods the room through bay windows, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. The ensuite bathroom is complete with double vanity sinks, a soaking tub, and a separate shower, providing both functionality and relaxation.

Step outside to your fully fenced yard, covered and screened patio a perfect retreat to unwind and take in the breathtaking views of the lake. Imagine sipping your morning coffee or hosting gatherings in this serene outdoor space.

But the allure doesn't stop there - Bainebridge Estates offers a wealth of amenities for residents. Dive into the refreshing pool, play at the playground, or enjoy a friendly game of basketball or tennis on the courts. This community is designed for those who appreciate the finer things in life.

Convenience is key, and this home's location ensures just that. Minutes away from the highway, Jacksonville International Airport, nature parks, fishing spots, and boating destinations, you'll find yourself at the center of it all. Downtown is just a short 15-20 minute drive, and the beaches are a mere 30 minutes away. *Ask about our preferred lender incentive up to 1% credit and about about interest rate buy down & Down Payment assistance program ** Schedule a private tour today!

Don't miss the chance to make this your own - a truly great place to call home.
